<div class="view-question">How would you like to calculate your flight travel?</div>	
	
	<div class="form-element-container padding-top-10">
		<div class="form-element">
			<input type="radio" name="method" value="flights" checked="checked" /><label for="method">By specific flights</label>
		</div>

		<div class="form-element">
			<input type="radio" name="method" value="miles" /><label for="method">By estimated number of miles traveled</label>
		</div>


		<div class="form-element">
			<input type="radio" name="method" value="fuel" /><label for="method">By estimated gallons of fuel</label>
		</div>

		<div class="form-element">
			<input type="radio" name="method" value="length" /><label for="method">By estimated average trip length</label>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="form-element-container padding-top-10">
		<label>Would you like to use the<br />Refractive Forcing Index?<span class="info help" data-toggle="popover" data-content="RFI factors in additional emissions besides carbon that are caused by burning fuel. <a href='http://www.ipcc.ch/' target='_blank'>Learn more from the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change</a> (IPCC)."></span></label>
		<div class="form-element">
			<input type="radio" name="use_rfi" value="true" /><span class=""> Yes</span><br />
			<input type="radio" name="use_rfi" value="false" class=""/><span class=""> No</span>
		</div>
	</div>
